{
  "stem": "24554.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the Russian-- actually not Russia, the Soviets, yes?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They cross the border, yes-- the so-called Curzon Line, you know, it was in the West Ukraine, yes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from [NON-ENGLISH] it was, I moved to Rowne, it was a small city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It Rowne, and around Rowne, you know, there was a lot of Czech people, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They move from Bohemia where is from the Czech, in the last century to Russia-- it belongs to Russia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They started on the farms, there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one condition was they must change their religion from Catholics, there was [NON-ENGLISH], you know-- Russian orthodox, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I come there and started work in a farm, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was September, October, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tell you, the trouble started after-- I don't know how many weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] how you say it-- [NON-ENGLISH] it was the interior police, you know-- the political police.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took us all around, you know, we was many hundred people around this town, Rowne, where we work, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the first thing they take from us, the documents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said-- they told us, you are illegal in the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, how we are illegal?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You crossed the border, not we.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I say, no, you are illegal, you don't have permission to stay in the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Said, you know, you have seen, we have a Czechoslovak passport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Say, yes, you have a Czechoslovak passport, but Czechoslovakia don't exist-- exist only protectorat Bohemia Moravia, and the Slovak independent state.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you are stateless, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what I don't know before never, you know, in Soviet Union exist Jewish nationality.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they accept I am Jewish nationality, you know, but not citizenship, yeah?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was without citizen-- only the nationality.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
